    <title>RADLogging</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><computeroutput><ref refid="namespaceRADLogging" kindref="compound">RADLogging</ref></computeroutput> is the beta logging layer for deployed RADLib applications.</para>
<para>Core features:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Async process-wide logger.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Severity levels and category filters.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Console, file, rotating file, and syslog sinks.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Streaming macros such as <computeroutput>RADLOG_INFO(&quot;category&quot;) &lt;&lt; &quot;message&quot;</computeroutput>. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
